&lt;p&gt;Cardiac Care on Bartholomew Unit is looking for a dynamic Band 5 Registered nurse to join our friendly and well supported team. We work closely together with the Cardiology Ward and Cardiac Catheter Suite to provide a high level of patient care for our patients. William Harvey’s Cardiac Care Unit is the Heart Centre for Kent providing immediate treatment for acute ST segment Myocardial Infarctions (pPCI), as well as Acute Coronary Syndrome, pacemakers, ICDs, CT angiograms, TOEs and general PCI. We pride ourselves on running an important service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please apply if you would like to join our friendly team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like to visit the Unit prior to an interview, please do not hesitate to contact Jennifer Hiatt-Gipson or Andrea Newbury, Ward Manager of Cardiac Care 01233 616115.&lt;/p&gt;
